    <description>
        <p><em>NymVPN</em> desktop application</p>
        <p>NymVPN is a decentralized, mixnet and and zero-knowledge VPN</p>

        <p>It provides the following features:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>5-hop <em>Anonymous</em> mode (using Nym <em>mixnet</em>)
            </li>
            <li>2-hop <em>Fast</em> mode (using <em>WireGuard</em>)
            </li>
            <li>No centralized logs</li>
            <li>Hide your public IP</li>
            <li>Entry and exit hop location</li>
        </ul>

        <p>NOTE: this package only provides the desktop <em>client</em> application.</p>
        <p>For the VPN to work, the <em>daemon</em> must be installed and running.</p>
        <p>We provide separate packages for the daemon:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>deb package (Nym repo): nym-vpnd</li>
            <li>AUR packages: nym-vpnd and nym-vpnd-bin</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more details, please check https://nymvpn.com/en/download/linux</p>
    </description>
